            <h2>Zeus</h2>
            <p class="subtitle" style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0;">King of the Gods, God of Sky and Thunder</p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Supreme ruler of Mount Olympus and the Greek pantheon, Zeus commands the sky, hurls thunderbolts, and upholds cosmic justice. As father of gods and men, he embodies sovereignty, law, and divine authority.</p>
        </section>

